{"tid":452422,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 近日下令禁止經銷商向伺服器級企業售賣GeForce顯示卡","createTime":"2017-10-30T08:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T03:31:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"96e5fa324a5e5072560a7eee84b01a1713f64040","tid":452422,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA近日明確下令，嚴禁將GeForce遊戲級顯示卡用於高效能計算、伺服器等專業領域。<br />\n<br />\n其實針對這些特殊領域，NVIDIA一直都有專門的產品，譬如說圖形工作站上的Quadro系列，高效能計算、深度學習方面的Tesla系列，但它們效能強勁的同時，價格也異常高昂。<br />\n<br />\n因此不少廠商就改而使用GeForce遊戲級顯示卡替代，畢竟本質上硬體是基本差不多的，還能大大節省成本。NVIDIA這幾年形勢不錯，GeForce、Quadro、Tesla各條產品線的收入都大幅上漲，但專業級顯示卡利潤更加豐厚，而為了避免產品線混亂、削弱利潤，NVIDIA已經定下了更嚴格的規定，不許將GeForce遊戲級顯示卡賣給專業廠商，或者用於專業領域。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，華碩、微星、技嘉等同時擁有顯示卡和業務的伙伴，將是NVIDIA的重點監視對象。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.xfastest.com/forum.php?mod=image&amp;aid=317958&amp;size=2000x550&amp;key=3b6cd03a8846bcc1&amp;type=fixnone\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dimage%26aid%3D317958%26size%3D2000x550%26key%3D3b6cd03a8846bcc1%26type%3Dfixnone&h=e44c5eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xfastest.com/thread-201880-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fthread-201880-1-1.html&d=HSI3DnjaSZfm9lPooOcGfYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7b82348f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xfastest.com/thread-201880-1-1.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"51465cc6626600a09cf1bfef6432c2aaa1ecb583","tid":452422,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA一貫強勢，因此規定一出，絕大多數AIC廠商、經銷商都會嚴格遵守，否則很容易被NVIDIA掐脖子、減少甚至停止供貨，得不償失。當然伺服器、工作站廠商就有點小麻煩了，採購成本肯定要大大增加。雖然AMD方面也有專業級顯示卡產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但無論效能還是技術支援都稍遜一籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"f9bc03ef3eb9523886b0a8b0a9e22e733b9c8356","tid":452422,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打橫嚟"},{"pid":"123cc86eeb325ea003c7706e20cc36521969f42d","tid":452422,"uid":79404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"A卡復興？"},{"pid":"5cf4f48179fac4e4d83f1d2787393ca411d202bf","tid":452422,"uid":144466,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"買黎點用關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd28d495850b38fa4952d3f43b30524cc086d11f","tid":452422,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"可以做中介賺錢"},{"pid":"cc5f6014d0941854b9ff4819c694a120dca75dec","tid":452422,"uid":78554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:40:16.000Z","msg":"屌垃圾n記惡過狗先係封virtualization 依家連點用賣俾邊個都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d9d74aad2a69bb7b199886d1e4050ce3342519","tid":452422,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45570155d82801bf78c0c80f2ce0bf13db760ff2","tid":452422,"uid":131884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"AMD係時候打劫市占率<br />\n股價重上14蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8eb0038e6593da6535b9a4f1745a21d850bda8","tid":452422,"uid":48276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c